BobUI for Linux/X11
----------------
 - QGtkStyle
    * Fixed rtl issues with sliders (BOBUIBUG-8986)
    * Fixed missing pressed appearance on scroll bar handles. (BOBUIBUG-10396)
    * Fixed crash when creating QGtkStyle before QApplication. (BOBUIBUG-10758)

 - QFontDatabase
    * [BOBUIBUG-4428] Fixed regression when using bitmap fonts on some 
      Linux systems.
 
 - QFontEngine
     * [BOBUIBUG-9442] Avoid possible square root of negative number in 
      FreeType font engine.
	  
 - QFontMetrics
    * [BOBUIBUG-10448] Fix crash when using fonts in non-gui QApplication.
	  
 	
BobUI for Windows
--------------
 - Popup windows now implicitly activate when shown. (BOBUIBUG-7386)
 - QComboBox [BOBUIBUG-7552] Fix an issue where only "..." would be shown for
   QComboBox with certain DPI settings.
 - Fixed a problem where menus exec'ed on system tray icons did not 
   disappear. (BOBUIBUG-7386)
 - Improved look and feel for QWizard on Windows 7 and Vista. (BOBUIBUG-9873), 
   (BOBUIBUG-11974) and (BOBUIBUG-6120)    
 - QLocalSocket
    * Pipe handle leak fixed, when closing a QLocalSocket that still has
      unwritten data. (BOBUIBUG-7815)
    * Fixed closing state for local sockets with unwritten data. (BOBUIBUG-9681)
    * Improved performance of writing to QLocalSocket.


BobUI for Mac OS X
---------------
 - QMacStyle
    * Removed frame around statusbar items. (BOBUIBUG-3574)
    * More native appearance of item view headers and frames. (BOBUIBUG-10047)
    * Increased spacing between tree view items. (BOBUIBUG-10190)
    * Removed frame around status bar items. (BOBUIBUG-3574)

 - QFontEngine	
    * Enable fractional metrics for the font engine on Mac in all 
      stages of text layout.
    * [BOBUIBUG-5529] Enable design metrics for correct character spacing 
      in ATSUI font engine. (Mac/Carbon)

- BOBUIextDocument
    * [BOBUIBUG-8791] Fix misalignment of fixed width fonts between 
      format changes on Cocoa.
	  
 - BOBUIextLayout
    * [BOBUIBUG-9879] Fix off-by-one in vertical position for elided and 
	  non-elided text.
 
BobUI for Embedded Linux
---------------------

