  * Add support for QFont::NoAntialias (BOBUIBUG-5936)

BobUI for Windows CE
-----------------

 - Core changes
    * Fixed menu handling on Windows mobile. (BOBUIBUG-8754)
    * Fixed a crash when receiving a certain type of WM_SETTINGSCHANGE
      message. (BOBUIBUG-7943)

 - QWindowsMobileStyle
    * Huge performance penalty for BOBUIabWidget fixed for
      Windows mobile 6.5. (BOBUIBUG-8419)
    * BOBUIabBar scroll button size has been fixed. (BOBUIBUG-8757)
    * Detection of Windows mobile 6.5 fixed. (BOBUIBUG-8418)

BobUI for Symbian
--------------

 - QSplashScreen
    * [BOBUIBUG-11129] Fixed a hanging bug in QSplashScreen on 3.1 devices.

 - QS60Main... classes
    * The future compatibility of QS60MainAppUi, QS60MainDocument and
      QS60MainApplication are improved by removing the need for any 
      sub-class to link to Avkon functions that may not exist in future.


